overview: Hasrat Bakar and Salimah to have a miscarriage when Salimah suffered miscarriage. Bakar desperate to find out who is the one who threw the garbage from the top floor of his flat house which resulted in the miscarriage of his wife's content. At the same time, their neighbors Rosnah feel very guilty as she knows this is all wrong.
title: Maaf Dari Khilaf
